Installing VDBVoxel Plugin
==================

Requirements
------------
- OpenVDB 3.0 and its all dependences
  http://www.openvdb.org/

- MODO software and MODO C++ SDK
  https://www.thefoundry.co.uk/products/modo/
  http://sdk.luxology.com/

Compilers that work for OpenVDB 3.0 should work for this plugin as well.
